summary about ActiveRecord

there is important relational between database and oop this relations is ORM
this enable developers to manipulate database record instead of writing alot of raw of queries

so there is a design pattern that encapsulating the complexities of relational db in object

the ActiveRecord is design patern that is solve three main problems 

--> main problems is 

1-CRUD operations
2-to save the results of queries in variable
3-manipulating the quries value

so the active Record make relations between the buisness logic and data presitences in single object

active record implementation not only useful to simplify the database interactions but ensure that developer do best practices while working with databases.

